description:
Anaconda is a 1997 action adventure horror film directed by Luis Llosa and written by Chris Broodryk. The film stars Jennifer Lopez, Ice Cube, Jon Voight, Eric Stoltz, Jonathan Hyde, and Owen Wilson. An international co-production between the United States and Brasil, the film focuses on a documentary film crew in the Amazon rainforest that is led by a snake hunter who is hunting down a giant, legendary green anaconda.

Voice Narration: Jon Bailey the EPIC VOICE GUY (@epicvoiceguy on all socials)
